            <div data-seq="186078603" data-index="3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t3"><span class="_j_anchor">景点:中轴线上的万春亭</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186061991">
            列位，景山公园地处<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城的中轴线上，占地23公顷。南与紫禁城的神武门隔街相望，西邻<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10796.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北海" target="_blank">北海</a>公园。景山山高42.6米，海拔88.35米，是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城的最高点。站在山顶可俯视全城，金碧辉煌的古老紫禁城与现代化的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>城新貌一览无余。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186055576" data-seq="186055592" data-pid="186055576" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186055576.html">
