                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186128188">
            列位、咱们往南看，那是中轴线上的皇冠，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>紫禁城。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186055581" data-seq="186055597" data-pid="186055581" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
