            <div id="_j_photo_186055587" data-seq="186055603" data-pid="186055587" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186055587.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/C7/wKgBZ1icF6OAY_FiAAnZOg7vnYM47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/C7/wKgBZ1icF6OAY_FiAAnZOg7vnYM47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186055587" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186063761">
            列位，因为景山公园的四座方亭都一样，在这里咱们只介绍[周赏亭]就可以了。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[周赏亭]为景山五方亭之一，与<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13033.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="山西" target="_blank">山西</a>侧的富览亭相对而建，其建筑形式和彩绘完全相同，周赏亭是在明代建筑的基础上于清乾隆十五年（1750年）兴建的，周赏亭为孔雀蓝琉璃瓦覆顶，紫晶色琉璃瓦剪边，是重檐攒尖的圆形古亭，&nbsp;亭高约为11.3米，&nbsp;建筑面积近100平方米。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186055588" data-seq="186055604" data-pid="186055588" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186055588.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/C8/wKgBZ1icF6SAVvoXAAnf41mEHpQ56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/C8/wKgBZ1icF6SAVvoXAAnf41mEHpQ56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186055588" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div data-seq="186079252" data-index="4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t3"><span class="_j_anchor">景点:明思宗自缢处</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186077407">
            列位，咱们来到的是明思宗自缢处。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;据记载，这里是明代崇祯皇帝自缢的地方。崇祯十七年（1644年）李自成率领农民起义军攻入<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>，崇祯皇帝见在势已去，来到景山写下遗诏，自缢在此处的槐树上。《明史帝纪》中记载：“丁末昧爽，内城陷，帝崩于万岁山，王承恩从死”。明末人李清在《三坦笔记》中记载：“遂同承恩对缢煤山古树下”。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186055590" data-seq="186055605" data-pid="186055590" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186055590.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/CA/wKgBZ1icF6aAMD3tAA_Z2mPZ93E41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/CA/wKgBZ1icF6aAMD3tAA_Z2mPZ93E41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186055590" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186077532">
            列位，为什么这棵大槐树有罪槐的说法呢？您听我慢慢道来。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;观妙亭下的槐树为景山一景，这倒并不是因为槐树本身长的多吸引人，而是其背后的故事，它与明朝灭亡的历史紧紧相连，就像一位朝代更迭的见证者，因而，人们纷至沓来，凭吊历史。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;清军入关后，为笼络人心，康熙皇帝派人给这棵老槐树栓上了一根大铁链，并称它为“罪槐”，意为朱由检正名，其罪所指之人是李自成，并规定清室皇族成员路过此地都要下马步行。1930年，故宫博物院延请沈尹默书写“明思宗殉国处”的石碑，1931年立于老槐树旁。后历经周折，这石碑破损后又经修复，立于原处。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;当然，现在观妙亭下的这棵槐树已经不是当年崇祯自缢那一棵，老槐在饱经沧桑之后已于1966年枯死，现在那棵槐树只是因历史之故后来补种的。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186056853" data-seq="186056868" data-pid="186056853" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186056853.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/56/wKgBZ1icGDqAZoR6ABXtqOMg1K860.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/56/wKgBZ1icGDqAZoR6ABXtqOMg1K860.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186056853" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_186056858" data-seq="186056873" data-pid="186056858" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186056858.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/66/wKgBZ1icGEeAPpQiABIAEeOjLYI45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/66/wKgBZ1icGEeAPpQiABIAEeOjLYI45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186056858" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_186056860" data-seq="186056875" data-pid="186056860" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186056860.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/69/wKgBZ1icGEqAbE7hAAp6YGSazq052.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/69/wKgBZ1icGEqAbE7hAAp6YGSazq052.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186056860" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186076499">
            [观德殿]位于寿皇殿东，明代时是帝王的习射之所。自清代乾隆起，便改为停放帝后的灵柩之处。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186056861" data-seq="186056876" data-pid="186056861" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186056861.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/6A/wKgBZ1icGEuAIyj6AApWSq-43bI28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/6A/wKgBZ1icGEuAIyj6AApWSq-43bI28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186056861" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_186056864" data-seq="186056879" data-pid="186056864" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186056864.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/70/wKgBZ1icGE-ANjorABHxCHdTLuE69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/70/wKgBZ1icGE-ANjorABHxCHdTLuE69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186056864" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186063881">
            列位，现在咱们来到了寿皇殿牌楼。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[寿皇殿]前的三座牌楼，是寿皇殿建筑群的重要组成部分，牌楼为四柱三洞九楼，黄色琉璃瓦覆顶，金丝楠木梁柱，额为乾隆御题，在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>皇家属最高等级的建筑形式，在皇家园林中独树一帜。<br />
牌楼建于清.乾隆十四年（1749年）曾于1947年大修，上世纪60年代也进行过修葺，2007年又进行了全面修缮和彩绘。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186056866" data-seq="186056881" data-pid="186056866" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186056866.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/74/wKgBZ1icGFGAIBagAAzLAoaA0qo09.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/53/74/wKgBZ1icGFGAIBagAAzLAoaA0qo09.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186056866" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div data-seq="186129654" data-index="5" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t3"><span class="_j_anchor">景点：中轴线上寿皇殿</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="186075214">
            [寿皇殿]位于景山正北方<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>古城中轴线上，垣墙呈方形，坐北朝南，有正殿、左右山殿、东西配殿，以及神厨、神库、碑亭、井亭等附属建筑。大殿正前方为戟门五楹。前为三个门洞的宫门，该门前有<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/84595.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="石狮" target="_blank">石狮</a>一对，另有三间四柱九楼雕兽夹杆石宝坊三座。左右山殿（衍庆殿，绵禧殿）各三楹，东西配殿各五楹。碑亭、井亭各两座，神厨、神库各五处。其全部建筑仿照太庙形式，布局严谨，庄肃堂皇，自成一体。<br />
[寿皇殿]是供明、清两代皇帝停灵、存放遗像和祭祖之所，即“神御殿”。明代该殿在景<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12976.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="山东" target="_blank">山东</a>北，清代顺治帝去世时其梓宫及骨灰曾停放在寿皇殿。后康熙帝将该殿作为检查射箭之所。康熙帝去世之后，其子雍正帝将其“御容”奉祀于该殿，后来乾隆帝又将其父雍正帝的“御容”供奉于该殿。当时该殿跨度仅三楹，乾隆帝决定将该殿作为奉祀“神御”之殿，开始了改造扩建工程。新的寿皇殿建筑群改建于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>古城南北中轴线上，共九楹，建筑规模和等级远超明代所建寿皇殿。(以上信息来自网络)<br />
[寿皇殿]原先一直由<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>少年宫占用，现已收回，正在维修中，我们在不久的将来可以目睹它的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10244.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="庐山" target="_blank">庐山</a>真面目了。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_186057804" data-seq="186057814" data-pid="186057804" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186057804.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/54/1B/wKgBZ1icGOCAVTHWAAouQDQjgj453.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/54/1B/wKgBZ1icGOCAVTHWAAouQDQjgj453.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186057804" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_186057805" data-seq="186057815" data-pid="186057805" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3562">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6643859/186057805.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/54/1B/wKgBZ1icGOCAbUriAAQZ-T79aSk73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/54/1B/wKgBZ1icGOCAbUriAAQZ-T79aSk73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="186057805" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3562.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3562" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>景山公园
                </a>
            </span>
